{"tid":2340631,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企過聖誕，自己整聖誕晚餐","createTime":"2020-12-25T15:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T07:20:55.000Z","uid":132749,"like":71,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1247a9124bac22ec57559f040263460df4683781","tid":2340631,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T15:53:53.000Z","msg":"今次聖誕餐，朋友黎食晚，無時間慢慢錄片， 淨係影左幾張相做記錄。 <br />\n<br />\n之前買左個斧頭扒，襯今次多人就整埋黎食<br />\n未醃之前， 已經將骨位既肉同筋膜去乾淨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hvJKL5W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhvJKL5W.jpg&h=60d5dfc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落黑椒，鹽，放雪櫃過夜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6RLMZsy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6RLMZsy.jpg&h=93cef453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBrine後<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zt68tmA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzt68tmA.jpg&h=c9af73cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n包返條骨去燒，廢事黑晒，110度燒一個鍾 拎出黎rest 後再火槍燒到有層焦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vuNzoVz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvuNzoVz.jpg&h=3923077c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外雞都係早有晚Brine 焗前一個鍾拎出黎回溫，同斧頭扒一齊入爐，焗到8成熟再用250焗熟佢，爛完無時間影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tGL5vBf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtGL5vBf.jpg&h=17607538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日整左4樣野，有個pork rib朋友拎過黎<br />\n<br />\nPepperoni pizza <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQjFjvr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQjFjvr.jpg&h=403d237c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGarlic prawn pizza<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yEBsJXo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyEBsJXo.jpg&h=436401e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n斧頭扒+ pork rib<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iwF9cRc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiwF9cRc.jpg&h=04dba83f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRoasted chicken <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MZnzoX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMZnzoX4.jpg&h=a5273650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DT2caC8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDT2caC8.jpg&h=7aaed133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外仲整左加個韓燒，有韓豬腩肉同牛肉，雜菜<br />\n<br />\n但無影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係得準備時牛肉porterhouse 切片時有影左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ofnLvEa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FofnLvEa.jpg&h=4fc3ad08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次無時間錄片，如果有興趣可以去我YouTube , 有其他整野食既片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYouTube: <a href=\"https://youtube.com/channel/UCGJHwItoXY4IkZX7efJvCXg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCGJHwItoXY4IkZX7efJvCXg&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=957f3e83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/channel/UCGJHwItoXY4IkZX7efJvCXg</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/openfridge_kitchendiary/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fopenfridge_kitchendiary%2F&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=0e200e2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/openfridge_kitchendiary/</a><br />\n<br />\nMEWE:<a href=\"https://mewe.com/i/openfridgekitchendiary\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fi%2Fopenfridgekitchendiary&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=d1159493\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/i/openfridgekitchendiary</a>"},{"pid":"648acfcf921cd66416a5d19194e5ec6082c8bbf8","tid":2340631,"uid":325677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T15:56:16.000Z","msg":"好勁 好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b81496eea7ee18eedd06a44fd4968c6e666471","tid":2340631,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"648acfcf921cd66416a5d19194e5ec6082c8bbf8","tid":2340631,"uid":325677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T15:56:16.000Z","msg":"好勁 好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:11:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尋日返工，都唔係好夠時間整，如果多時間d會整埋甜品同整好小小，"},{"pid":"1e15f0e0270218641a27d5758e9d0aa0ab554ab9","tid":2340631,"uid":154373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:13:46.000Z","msg":"放棄木狗 改睇你鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f538dc1d4d70eff4de690e1abd8dec9c527fe8a1","tid":2340631,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e15f0e0270218641a27d5758e9d0aa0ab554ab9","tid":2340631,"uid":154373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:13:46.000Z","msg":"放棄木狗 改睇你鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:21:07.000Z","msg":"邊個係木狗？"},{"pid":"42974b858e7fe7015d95ec8730a2930381d82b1b","tid":2340631,"uid":363579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:23:04.000Z","msg":"好正<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea48be96a18077e1a793e20c4b27b6c3cbc31a3f","tid":2340631,"uid":154373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f538dc1d4d70eff4de690e1abd8dec9c527fe8a1","tid":2340631,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e15f0e0270218641a27d5758e9d0aa0ab554ab9","t