631,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb8f039d36dffe85d80ca46a6cfdb134fb39b43a","tid":2340631,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T18:18:51.000Z","msg":"Pizza looks jeng<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T00:33:02.000Z","msg":"Pizza 今次加厚左個皮，我自己覺得好食d,  上次拍個個Margarita 就薄皮。    另外今次個pepperoni 無用baking stone 整， 太林，後來去補救，試到個方法整到個底硬身返好多。 同街食到既一樣，正好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGarlic prawns 就用返baking stone 再加新方法去整脆個底， 勁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a04cfa2098c0aedc47e1950495bbcf03b39d39c","tid":2340631,"uid":227988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T00:37:14.000Z","msg":"好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dabac52a136f760ae4f458b91933278e1baf047","tid":2340631,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69b62a92c59e629d5a0793fc8d028fc7077dd0e8","tid":2340631,"uid":362121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T18:25:51.000Z","msg":"Domino&rsquo;s garlic prawn?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T00:37:43.000Z","msg":"我無食過Domino garlic prawns. 我次次都食最平個d， 食domino為頂肚。 事但平平地飽就算。 <br />\n<br />\n宜個我都係朋友鍾意食蝦，我就自己整左garlic butter 加parsley 去醃蝦， 加salt  &amp; pepper, lemon juice. 最後就連garlic butter 放埋落pizza度。 第一次整，但出黎好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"c7133bb33871500b4345d47f8d0e32b9a05da7cf","tid":2340631,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2078c089e82ef19d3ff696b7e009b55d75bf7267","tid":2340631,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T19:47:57.000Z","msg":"返工整唔到咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都好多囉，全部都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/